## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and does not include any studies or findings published after this date. Additionally, the effectiveness of vaccines can vary based on new strains of diseases and ongoing research, which may not be fully captured in this report. The findings are also limited to the sources reviewed and may not encompass all perspectives or recent developments in vaccine research.